@NODE "History" "History"
@NEXT "Main"
@PREV "Thank-Yous"
@{CODE}@{JCENTER}@{APEN 2}History
@{jleft}@{apen 1}
V1.0 - Initial release as SmMWBIcons.LHA on Aminet

v2.0 - First release was done in a hurry and not well organized.
     - Renamed the collection as "MagicStartMenu.LHA"
     - Created an Installer script
     - Added more .bru files
     - Modified MWB .bru files the came with StartMenu v2.0
     - Changed the logo designs a bit
     - Changed the Startb.bru, because I really thought the previous one was ugly.
     - Changed the StartMenu icon to reflect the Startb.bru design.
     - Created an AmigaGuide text document

v2.1 - Forgot to include the new Startb.bru in the previous archive. Opps!
     - The StartMenu icon was saved as a Project icon, rather than a Tool.  Fixed.
     - Added more brush (.bru) files.
     - New AudMon brushes created that fit more into the MWB XEN style.

v2.2 - Created new logos
     - Still wasn't happy with the startbutton image, so I created a new check-
       mark image.  NOW I'm happy. ;-)
     - Changed MWB drawer and icons to match new checkmark image.
     - Included new Miami.bru image
     - Shortened Window.bru by one pixel line.

v2.3 - Looks like no more StartMenu updates from John Corigliano; his HD crashed :-(
     - Update the Amiga checkmark to the proper look.
     - Added 16 colour variations of some images (I got myself a new graphics board!)
     - Added new images/brushes.
     - Updated installation script.
     - Slightly modified the Guide document.
     - Added new 800x600x256 colour image of my Workbench!
@ENDNODE

